quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  8,53,"(Ko wa…ói) …óum, ko tawde Alla wonaani bayloowo dokke mo rokki e yim…ďe haa …ďe mbayla ko woni e woŇčkiiji ma…ď…ďe. E wonnde pellet, Alla ko Nanoowo ganndu…óo."
  8,54,"Wano mboowdi yim…ďe Fir'awna e …ďen adinoo…ďe …ďe. ∆Āe njeddi Aayeeje Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óeen. min kalkiri …ďe bakkatuuji ma…ď…ďe …ói, Men njooli yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďeen. Kala (ma…ď…ďe) laatino too√Īoo…ďe."
  8,55,"Pellet, ko …ďuri bonnde e ko ruugata kon ka Alla, ko …ďeen yeddu…ďe, kam…ďe …ďe ngooŇč…óintaa."
  8,56,"∆Āeen …ďe ahodi…óaa e mu'm refti …ďe firta ahadi ma…ď…ďe ndiin e kala laawol, kam…ďe …ďe kulataa [Alla]."
  8,57,"Si waawii …ďe ka hare, yagginir (sar) …ďe aroo…ďe …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe. mbejo'o, …ďe mbaajitora …ďe"
  8,58,"Ammaa si a hulii e yim…ďe jamfa, bugita(werla) e ma…ď…ďe (firtugol ahadi ndin) dow potondiral, tawde pellet, Alla yi…óaa jamfotoo…ďe …ďeen."
  8,59,"Wota …ďeen yeddu…ďe cikku …ďe laawki. Pellet, kam…ďe …ďe ronknitaa (kam)."
  8,60,"Keplanee(heblanee) …ďe kala ko kattan…óon e doole e pucci kebilaa…ói, kul…ďiniron …óuum a√Ī…ďe Alla …ďeen e a√Ī…ďe mon …ďeen, e wo…ó…ďe goo gaanin ma…ď…ďe …ďe onon on nganndaabe Alla ka√Īum no anndi …ďe. Kala ko nafkudon e laawol Alla ngol timminate on, onon on too√Īoytaake.(hay huude)"
  8,61,"Si …ďe naayanike kisal nagl, naayano ngal (an kadi) pawo…óaa e Alla, pellet, KaŇčko ko O nanoowo ganndu…óo."